<h2>27 Features Available in the Dataset</h2>
<p>Our dataset contains 27 different features,
ranging from temperature and pressure to sub-surface soil temperature and moisture levels.
</p>
<ol class="list-group  mt-5">
  <li class="list-group-item">Temperature, Dewpoint Temperature</li>
  <li class="list-group-item">Soil Temperature Layer 1-4</li>
  <li class="list-group-item">Volumetric Soil Water Layer 1-4</li>
  <li class="list-group-item">Surface [Thermal, Solar, Diffuse] Radiation</li>
  <li class="list-group-item">Relative Humidity</li>
  <li class="list-group-item">Surface Pressure, Sea Level Pressure</li>

  <li class="list-group-item">Total Cloud Cover</li>
  <li class="list-group-item">Total Precipitation </li>
  <li class="list-group-item">Snowfall, Snow Depth, Snow Density</li>

  <li class="list-group-item">Wind Speed, Direction, 10m Gust, 100m Speed & Direction</li>

</ol>


<div class="mt-5">
<p>
Layer depths (for soil temperature and moisture)
</p>
<ul class="list-group">
  <li class="list-group-item">Layer 1 (0 - 7cm) - (0 - 2.75 inches)</li>
  <li class="list-group-item">Layer 2 (7 - 28cm) - (2.75 - 11 inches)</li>
  <li class="list-group-item">Layer 3 (28 - 100cm) - (11 - 39.4 inches)</li>
  <li class="list-group-item">Layer 4 (100 - 289cm) - (39.4 - 113.4 inches)</li>
</ul>
</div>



